Initial commit features

  - preview
  - status message
  - exit button
  - screen keep on
  - no window title
  - localserver and local sockets (not used)
  - test feature: video streaming into socket (192.168.1.51:8081)
  - video settings: MPEG_4 + H263, 640x480
  - video encoding bit rate: 1024 ** 2
  - audio settings: AAC
  - audio encoding bit rate: 320000
  - audio sampling rate: 48000

Bugs:
  - samsung freezing
  - no audio
  - video too fast
  - fatal error if server is not running

